                     <interp inst="t18230115-87-person831" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I keep the Bell, public-house, in Warwick-lane. On Wednesday night, I saw the prisoner go down my yard, with this side of pork on his arm. I<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182301150038"></xptr>followed, and took him in Warwick-lane, and gave him in charge. I compared it with the fellow side, at the prosecutors - it fitted, and he said he took it from there.</p>
               <p>The prisoner pleaded distress.</p>
